                     <interp inst="t18280221-266-person1510" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was given into my charge.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was rather intoxicated; I took the meat, and threw it down, not with any felonious intention; I offered to pay for it when they took me - I did not move from the place.</p>
               <p>
